github-actions[bot] opened issue #11633:

fxhash - no longer maintained

Details
Status unmaintained
Package fxhash
Version 0.2.1
URL https://github.com/cbreeden/fxhash/issues/20
Date 2025-09-05

The fxhash crate is no longer maintained.

The repository is stale and owner is no longer active on GitHub.

Please take a look at rustc-hash instead.

See [advisory page](https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2025-0057.html) for additional details.

~~~

pchickey commented on issue #11633:

Triage: this gets pulled in through fxprof-processed-profile, a dep of wasmtime which is optional, enabled with profiling, and enabled as part of the default features.
